@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lusxfc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(0.49)
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.96) * 0.79) * 0.97)
    tmp = 0.72
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.30) - tmp)
    tmp = 0.70
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.sin((tmp + 0.46 / v2 + 0.21)))
    data[tid] = v0
